---
title: Extra Cheesy Mushroom & Bacon Spaghetti Boscaiola with Rocket & Pear Salad
description: This spaghetti dish pairs the earthy flavours of mushrooms with an easy creamy sauce. The side salad balances the richness of
the pasta with a sweet and juicy pear.

*We’ve replaced fettuccine in this recipe with spaghetti due to
ingredient availability. It’ll be just as delicious, just follow your recipe!*

image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/66f4f226587dccd5cb5f1efd-be69f3c0.jpeg
